  <h1>Important Notices</h1>
  <div class="meta">EDU Mileage+ &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Last updated: April 28, 2026</div>
</header>

<main>

  <div class="info-box warning">
    <strong>Please read carefully.</strong> This page contains important
    disclaimers regarding accuracy, tax implications, and recordkeeping
    responsibility. Use of EDU Mileage+ indicates acceptance of these notices in
    addition to Apple&rsquo;s standard End User License Agreement.
  </div>

  <nav class="toc" aria-label="Table of contents">
    <p>Contents</p>
    <ol>
      <li><a href="#accuracy">Accuracy and No Warranty</a></li>
      <li><a href="#tax">Tax Information Disclaimer</a></li>
      <li><a href="#recordkeeping">Recordkeeping Responsibility</a></li>
      <li><a href="#trademarks">Trademarks</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ol>
